From: Sebastian Mendel <sebastian.mendel@netresearch.de>
Date: Thu, 25 Sep 2025 12:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] ci: drop Go 1.23 support to match testcontainers v0.39.0 requirements

- testcontainers-go v0.39.0 requires Go 1.24 as minimum version
- Updated CI matrix to test only Go 1.24 and 1.25
- Aligns with go.mod which already specifies go 1.24.0

---
 .github/workflows/optimized-tests.yml | 6 +++---
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/.github/workflows/optimized-tests.yml b/.github/workflows/optimized-tests.yml
index abc1234..def5678 100644
--- a/.github/workflows/optimized-tests.yml
+++ b/.github/workflows/optimized-tests.yml
@@ -13,7 +13,7 @@ jobs:
     runs-on: ubuntu-latest
     strategy:
       matrix:
-        go-version: ['1.23', '1.24', '1.25']
+        go-version: ['1.24', '1.25']

     steps:
     - name: Checkout code
@@ -55,7 +55,7 @@ jobs:
     runs-on: ubuntu-latest
     strategy:
       matrix:
-        go-version: ['1.23', '1.24', '1.25']
+        go-version: ['1.24', '1.25']

     steps:
     - name: Checkout code
@@ -223,7 +223,7 @@ jobs:
     runs-on: ubuntu-latest
     strategy:
       matrix:
-        go-version: ['1.23', '1.24', '1.25']
+        go-version: ['1.24', '1.25']

     steps:
     - name: Checkout code